headline: Has EMCOR Group’s 51% Surge Left Further Room After Q1 2025 Earnings Beat?
summary: If you have been watching EMCOR Group’s stock climb, you are probably asking yourself, “Is there still room to run, or have I missed the boat?” Over the past year, shares have soared by 51.2%, capping off a stunning five-year rally of 846.2%. Even in the last three years, EMCOR Group has delivered an eye-catching 424.2% return.
